<exercise id="fs-id1169738039225">
<problem id="fs-id1169738039227">
<para id="fs-id1169738039229">What is the physical meaning of <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>h</m:mi><m:mo>′</m:mo></m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> What are the units?</para>
